wiki.summary: "Swalla" is a song recorded by American singer Jason Derulo featuring rapper Nicki Minaj and singer Ty Dolla Sign. It was released on February 24, 2017, by Warner Bros. Records, as the first single from Derulo's upcoming fifth studio album. The song was written by Derulo, Minaj, Ty, Ricky Reed, LunchMoney Lewis, Robert Diggs, Jacob Kasher Hindlin, Robin Weisse and Russell Jones. Derulo previewed "Swalla" in a video posted in August 2016. He officially announced it as a single on January 2, 2017. Read more on Last.fm.
